org.activity.generator

Class DatabaseCreatorGowallaQuickerPreprocessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.activity.generator.DatabaseCreatorGowallaQuickerPreprocessor

  • public class DatabaseCreatorGowallaQuickerPreprocessor
extends java.lang.Object
    To generate data with category information.
    This class takes as input the raw obtained data. The generated (processed) data from this class is then further processed and filtered using R. The resultant subset of data selected in R will then be used to create the databases to be used for experiments.
    Reads Note: we are setting the time zone to be UTC as the raw data is in UTC
    Author:
    gunjan
